---
import IconCardButton from "./icons/IconCardButton.astro";
import IconGithub from "./icons/IconGithub.astro";
import IconLinkedin from "./icons/IconLinkedin.astro";
---

<footer
    id="contacto"
    class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-5xl mx-auto p-6 md:p-12 mt-20 mb-10 border-t border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl"
>
    <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-8 mb-12"
    >
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
                ¿Trabajamos juntos?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-md">
                Estoy disponible para nuevas oportunidades. Si tienes un
                proyecto en mente o buscas sumar a alguien con mi perfil a tu
                equipo, no dudes en escribirme.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col justify-around gap-8">
            <div>
                <a
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aldo-leonel-zunino-becerra/"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-purple-600 rounded-full hover:bg-purple-700 hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(147,51,234,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(147,51,234,0.6)]"
                >
                    Escribime a Linkedin
                    <IconCardButton class="w-8 h-8 ml-2" />
                </a>
            </div>

            <div>
                <a
                    href="mailto:zunino.aldo@gmail.com"
                    class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white transition-all duration-300 bg-purple-600 rounded-full hover:bg-purple-700 hover:scale-105 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(147,51,234,0.4)] hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(147,51,234,0.6)]"
                >
                    Enviame un Email
                    <IconCardButton class="w-8 h-8 ml-2" />
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-white/10 my-8" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
        <div class="flex gap-6">
            <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/aldo-leonel-zunino-becerra/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-gray-400 hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors"
            >
                <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
                <IconLinkedin class="w-6 h-6" />
            </a>
            <a
                href="https://github.com/ZuninoAldo"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="text-gray-400 hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors"
            >
                <span class="sr-only">GitHub</span>
                <IconGithub class="w-6 h-6" />
            </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 text-center md:text-right">
            &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Aldo Leonel Zunino Becerra.<br
                class="block md:hidden"
            /> Todos los derechos reservados.
        </p>
    </div>
</footer>
